WEBVTT
NOTE OE3D — Script3 — English

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.484
Hello!

2
00:00:01.434 --> 00:00:05.900
The skin in contact with your prosthesis or orthosis deserves special attention.

3
00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:09.227
Good skin hygiene prevents most complications.

4
00:00:09.227 --> 00:00:11.483
Here are the right habits to adopt.

5
00:00:12.883 --> 00:00:14.634
Daily hygiene.

6
00:00:14.584 --> 00:00:19.838
Every evening, wash the skin in contact with your device with warm water and a mild pH-neutral soap.

7
00:00:19.838 --> 00:00:23.885
Rinse thoroughly and dry gently by dabbing, without rubbing.

8
00:00:23.885 --> 00:00:25.802
This step is essential.

9
00:00:27.202 --> 00:00:28.720
Prevention.

10
00:00:28.670 --> 00:00:33.066
Moisturize the skin after cleaning, but never just before putting on the device.

11
00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:37.974
Avoid skin folds in the device, and wear suitable underwear without thick seams.

12
00:00:39.374 --> 00:00:41.065
Warning signs.

13
00:00:41.015 --> 00:00:49.179
Contact us right away if you notice redness lasting more than twenty minutes, a wound, a pressure sore, an unusual smell or abnormal swelling.

14
00:00:49.179 --> 00:00:51.191
Never ignore these signs.

15
00:00:52.591 --> 00:00:54.988
Your comfort is our priority.

16
00:00:54.938 --> 00:00:57.841
Our team is here to support you at every step.

17
00:00:57.841 --> 00:00:59.949
Do not hesitate to contact us.
